# Title: Access To ADMIN$ Network Share
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2017-03-04
# Level: low
# Description: Detects access to ADMIN$ network share
# MITRE Tactic: Lateral Movement
# Tags: attack.lateral-movement, attack.t1021.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_admin_share_access.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administrative activity

EventID=5140 ShareName="Admin$" NOT SubjectUserName="*$"